      <title>亚马逊将停止向开发者支付为 Alexa 创建应用程序的费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/amazon-to-stop-paying-developers-to-create-apps-for-alexa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司将不再向开发人员支付为 Alexa 创建应用程序的费用，从而放弃了该公司为其语音激活数字助理打造繁荣的应用程序商店的努力的一个关键要素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/amazon-to-stop-paying-developers-to-create-apps-for-alexa</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 14:19:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
