      <title>在 1 万亿美元的 AI 反弹之后，Meta 交易以折扣价进行七巨头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/meta-trades-at-a-discount-to-magnificent-seven-after-1-trillion-ai-rally</link>
